casebody.data:
John Roberts, Plaintiff in Error, v. State of Florida, Defendant in Error. R. H. Buford and Amos E. Lewis, for Plaintiff in Error. Park Trammell, Attorney General, for the State.

Writ of error to a judgment of the Circuit Court of Liberty County.

Writ of error dismissed on November 7th, 1912, on motion of counsel for plaintiff in error.
